{"tid":2358466,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"獨厚師妹子瑜不爽了！Rain爆料反遭恩師揭「隱藏秘密」","createTime":"2021-01-08T07:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T11:01:52.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84c3e692ad4a551a07f88d977f0765cd777fd09e","tid":2358466,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:10:56.000Z","msg":"天王RAIN與朴軫永近期推出合作單曲《Switch to me》，日前更作客人氣綜藝節目《認識的哥哥》，談到合作契機，Rain透露主要是收到粉絲要求希望能透過朴軫永寫的歌回歸，才向朴軫永開口，沒想到朴軫永竟在節目中大爆料，透露「Rain賺的錢，早在進軍美國時都敗光了」，大揭Rain長久以來「隱藏的秘密」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/04/2968156-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F04%2F2968156-PH.jpg&h=cf956a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Rain（左）與朴軫永近期推出合作單曲《Switch to me》，一起作客《認識的哥哥》。（圖／friDay影音提供）<br />\n<br />\nRain與朴軫永這對師徒組合，近日推出合作單曲《Switch to me》，這也是Rain時隔13年後，再次唱朴軫永寫的歌。對此，朴軫永形容寫完歌後，整個人都相當興奮，認為這首歌真是絕了！但在播放給Rain聽後，突然覺得這首歌太一般，「明明昨晚睡前覺得很棒，怎麼今天卻是另外一種感覺？」他又說：「果不其然Rain的表情也不太好！」於是朴軫永拿了自己預定在秋天回歸寫的歌， Rain聽了後，直喊：「這就是我想唱的！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/04/2968155-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F04%2F2968155-PH.jpg&h=56770c61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Rain（左）與朴軫永在節目中唇槍舌戰，火藥味十足。（圖／friDay影音提供）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/04/2968154-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F04%2F2968154-PH.jpg&h=97f9d3a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但Rain也透露，在練習生時期簡直就像在軍隊裡，有一次過生日，就和其它練習生在炸雞店門口，飯都還沒吃，就被老闆朴軫永撞見，當下被訓了一個多小時，「你現在是做這些的時候嗎？」反觀後來的師妹Wonder Girls和Twice過生日，朴軫永還送禮物，唯獨對他特別嚴苛，讓Rain忍不住當面怒嗆朴軫永：「如果我沒成功，公司（指JYP娛樂）就不可能存在的！」朴軫永則回擊：「每個人都會這樣認為，但隱藏的秘密是，Rain賺的錢，在進軍美國時都敗光了！」《認識的哥哥》每周日於friDay影音全網首播。"},{"pid":"5727f665d49a99a25ce2353601dc3da6831ae570","tid":2358466,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"佢兩個感情好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7dc886070a8a37981822fe4f96d01d669c2f416","tid":2358466,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5727f665d49a99a25ce2353601dc3da6831ae570","tid":2358466,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"佢兩個感情好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"真兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b5aaa076291d0a6a8674372075f9fa564a5d6f","tid":2358466,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"成篇嘢都無提子瑜"},{"pid":"c9060f11321a06c98a557f2bc4535710c2b3c138","tid":2358466,"uid":316152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b5aaa076291d0a6a8674372075f9fa564a5d6f","tid":2358466,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"成篇嘢都無提子瑜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:00:49.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9x9sk3c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9x9sk3c.gif&h=5784bd22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5813a35675cb47ea4709b3255aac7397dc41e61d","tid":2358466,"uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:01:52.000Z","msg":"Rain（左）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}